# AGENTS.md Maintenance

Follow `docs/policy/agents-md-policy.md` for the full policy. Key rules:

- Keep total file under 150 lines, each section under 50 lines
- Commands section first: exact invocations, not prose descriptions
- No duplication across tiers (AGENTS.md, `.cursor/rules/`, `docs/policy/`)
- No secrets, tokens, branch names, or transient details
- `Learned User Preferences` and `Learned Workspace Facts` are maintained by `continual-learning` — do not hand-edit
- Skills table must reflect current `.cursor/skills/` contents
